data.description: Welcome to 490 Trebisky, a stunning three-bedroom, two-full-bath brick ranch nestled on an expansive acre lot in the heart of Richmond Heights. Boasting a desirable open floor plan, this home is perfect for modern living and entertaining. Step inside to discover a beautifully updated interior featuring new LTV flooring throughout, complemented by a neutral color palette that enhances the sense of space and light. The kitchen is a chef's dream, showcasing sleek stainless steel appliances, stylish countertops, and ample cabinetry for storage. Retreat to the owners suite, complete with a renovated ensuite bath for ultimate relaxation. Additional highlights include a sunroom, ideal for enjoying the picturesque views of the sprawling backyard, as well as a convenient shed for extra storage. With a newer roof and an invisible pet fence already in place, this home offers both peace of mind and endless possibilities. Don't miss your chance to own this one-of-a-kind property in a prime location.
